kquote><blockquote>雖然反共<br />\n<br />\n但我接觸唔少大陸客<br />\n人地真係態度好過香港人好多</blockquote><br />\n反共+1<br />\n雖然大陸人講野好嘈好大聲<br />\n但起碼唔會黑住面同你講野<br />\n又唔會多多要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那人係煩<br />\n但你可以大大聲喝佢地<br />\n<br />\n香港人你大聲少少都嘈到你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過對住啲閪客我都會借其他客屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過大大聲話返大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人都試過駁返佢轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢應該以為我唔敢出聲由佢鬧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走個時仲一路行一路鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n排佢後面啲客仲同我講唔使咁嬲 唔使理啲無聊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正有家教 有錢 拎黑卡個啲根本唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9ff15bb2f6819cd6799411c9ecac9909f2f0d5","tid":26192,"uid":443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"香港客有咁差咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我預到既大部分都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係有啲煩習慣 例如 乜柒都要拎新 係個盒入面都要拎 呢度無都要問隔離舖拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同部分排得耐/一做錯少少野就閪面<br />\n但禮貌上無咩問題<br />\n<br />\n大陸客有啲會扔錢唔排隊 同好鍾意話買咁多比啲折佢 但同佢講返 佢會 對不起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 做左年幾旅遊景點sales"},{"pid":"532d0e1eb65659c8e7ba3f7c2dbbf7817771e649","tid":26192,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次係街度買嘢，<br />\n見到有一個港嬸，拎住兩件一模一樣樣但唔同顏色嘅貨，問過職員兩樣野究竟有乜分別。<br />\n個職員答佢只係得顏色唔同，佢屌個職員話呢個唔係佢想要嘅答案，答非所問。<br />\n<br />\n我心諗，唔通你要拎去化驗所驗有咩成份唔同咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452ed88af15105ad75ec913b10a868fa684a2d76","tid":26192,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港客同中蟈客其實差唔多<br />\n最撚閪一撚定係印度客 沒有之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTotally agree with u</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時爆膨直頭叫d 阿叉 comeback later<br />\n就算無客都唔會理佢，真係仆街黎<br />\n人又多，一個人睇野成棚人塞住<br />\n又臭，d 細路又馬騮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有最叻既就係R野，勁過港客，佢地真係可以R到最後一口氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要阿a 叫你拎 b 貨睇，阿b 叫你拎c 貨，跟住c 又話要睇d 貨show me show me，嘈到墟咁，又rude<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,完全感受到印度嗰種髒臭亂<br />\n<br />\n香港人都係普普通通，講閪印度客百份百係閪客"},{"pid":"fa9375489d110002b9db56096d42af6fbe9ad204","tid":26192,"uid":443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港客有咁差咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我預到既大部分都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係有啲煩習慣 例如 乜柒都要拎新 係個盒入面都要拎 呢度無都要問隔離舖拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同部分排得耐/一做錯少少野就閪面<br />\n但禮貌上無咩問題<br />\n<br />\n大陸客有啲會扔錢唔排隊 同好鍾意話買咁多比啲折佢 但同佢講返 佢會 對不起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 做左年幾旅遊景點sales</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充埋 最閪一定係印巴之類 無禮貌 無公德 閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473f5cc8f40496f45e4bc1c57e3fcb2b576d734e","tid":26192,"uid":56808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agree,閪客來講老女人真係世界級，十個有九個都勁難服侍，小家又孤寒，大陸人要求少快來快走都還好。<br